British Chanceller Says U.K. Will Introduce a Carbon Price Floor for Power

-- B y   J e n n i f e r   R y a n
-- 
2011-03-23T13:09:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-23/british-chanceller-says-u-k-will-introduce-a-carbon-price-floor-for-power.html
U.K. Chancellor of the Exchequer
 George Osborne  said the government would set a floor for carbon
prices.  “Today we become the first country in the world to
introduce a carbon price floor for the power sector,” he said
in Parliament today in  London . He also said green taxes would
rise as a share of total revenue.’’  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jennifer Ryan in London at 
